<P>When we came there, we found that Side <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="OXF" EXTENT="1 word"> the Pri&s;on very full of Friends, who were P<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="OXF" EXTENT="1+ letters">+&s;oners there before (as indeed were, at that ti<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="OXF" EXTENT="1+ letters"> all the other Parts of that Pri&s;on, and mo&s;t of t<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="OXF" EXTENT="1+ letters"> other Pri&s;ons about the Town) and our Addi<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="OXF" EXTENT="1+ letters">+on cau&s;ed a great Throng on that Side. No<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="OXF" EXTENT="1 letter">+with&s;tanding
