<LG>
<L>While I had thus been breathing forth my Grief,</L>
<L><GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="OXF" EXTENT="1 word"> hopes thereby to get me &s;ome Relief;</L>
<L><GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="OXF" EXTENT="1 letter"> heard, methought, his Voice &s;ay, <HI>Cea&s;e to Mourn:</HI></L>
<L><HI>Live. And though the Vail of Fle&s;h once worn,</HI></L>
