<HEAD><MILESTONE N="1663" UNIT="date"> <HI>E&s;t VITA caduca.</HI></HEAD>
<LG>
<L>AS is the fragrant Flower in the Field,</L>
<L>Which in the Spring a plea&s;ant Smell doth yield,</L>
<L>And lovely Sight; but &s;oon is withered:</L>
<L>So's MAN; to Day alive, to Morrow dead.</L>
