<L>Death rounds him in the Ear, <HI>Friend, thou mu&s;t Dye.</HI></L>
</LG>
<LG>
<L>Or like a Shadow in a Sunny Day,</L>
<L>Which in a Moment vani&s;heth away;</L>
<L>Or like a Smile, or Spark; &s;uch is the Span</L>
<L>Of Life, allow'd this <HI>Microco&s;m,</HI> MAN.</L>
